Terms of Service for Aether Bot

Welcome to the Terms of Service for Aether Bot. This document outlines the rules and guidelines for using Aether Bot, ensuring a fair and enjoyable experience for all users. By using Aether Bot, you agree to comply with these terms.

Conditions
These terms and conditions apply to every user and server that utilizes Aether Bot. By adding Aether Bot to your server or authorizing it as a User App, you agree to these terms of service, as well as any future updates or modifications that may be made. Continued use of Aether Bot constitutes acceptance of these terms.

Terms of Use
Prohibited Actions

Intentional command spam or attempts to crash or disrupt Aether Bot are strictly prohibited.

Aether Bot must not be used in servers dedicated to bot spam or command abuse.

User Responsibility

You are responsible for any violations of these terms caused by you or your server members.

Misuse of Aether Bot, including but not limited to exploitation of bugs or unauthorized modifications, is not allowed.

Rights of the Aether Team

The Aether Team reserves the right to prohibit any server or user from using Aether Bot for any reason, including violations of these terms.

We may update these terms of service at any time. Notice of significant changes will be provided in the official support server or through other appropriate channels.

Fair Usage

Aether Bot is intended for legitimate use only. Any activity that disrupts the bot's functionality or negatively impacts other users is not permitted.

Changes to Terms
The Aether Team reserves the right to modify these terms of service at any time. Users will be notified of significant changes, and continued use of Aether Bot after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.

Contact
If you have any questions or concerns regarding these terms, please contact the Aether Team through the official support server or designated contact channels.

By using Aether Bot, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms of service. Thank you for using Aether Bot responsibly!

